    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言延长最后期限后，TikTok 恢复服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/tiktok-to-restore-service-after-trump-vows-to-extend-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 于周日开始在美国恢复服务，此前经历了一系列事件，这款视频应用程序兑现了关闭的威胁，但当选总统唐纳德·特朗普却暂停了法律的执行，并宣布将给 TikTok 所有者三个月的时间寻找买家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/tiktok-to-restore-service-after-trump-vows-to-extend-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 17:39:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国总统如何行使强大的赦免权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/presidential-pardons-how-us-leaders-use-their-mighty-clemency-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统的赦免权是宪法中最绝对、最容易被误解的条款之一。正如亚历山大·汉密尔顿所写，赦免权源于公元七世纪英国国王的“赦免特权”，开国元勋们希望拥有强有力的赦免权，以便司法系统“轻松获得有利于不幸有罪的例外”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/presidential-pardons-how-us-leaders-use-their-mighty-clemency-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱德曼称通货膨胀和就业恐慌加剧国内动乱风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/inflation-and-job-scares-fuel-risk-of-civil-unrest-edelman-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[传播公司爱德曼称，全球通胀恐慌和经济变化会侵蚀就业的担忧加剧了人们认为世界变得越来越不公平的看法，并有可能引发国内骚乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/inflation-and-job-scares-fuel-risk-of-civil-unrest-edelman-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
